jasima.shopSim.core
Class SimpleJobShopExperiment

java.lang.Object
  jasima.core.experiment.Experiment
      jasima.shopSim.core.SimpleJobShopExperiment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Callable<Map<String,Object>>
Direct Known Subclasses:
HolthausSimple2Experiment, MimacExperiment, StaticShopExperiment
public abstract class SimpleJobShopExperiment
extends Experiment

Base class for shop experiments. This class wraps a SimpleJobShop. Derived classes will typically populate the shop with machines and JobSources and add functionality to collect some statistics and produce appropriate experiment results.

Author:
Torsten Hildebrandt, 2010-03-12
